Name: Papa Murphy's Holdings, Inc
Description: Papa Murphy's Holdings, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, owns, operates, and franchises Take ?N' Bake pizza stores. The company operates in three segments: Franchise, Company Stores, and Brand Funds. As of December 31, 2018, it operated approximately 1,437 stores, including 1,294 franchised and 106 company-owned stores in 37 states, as well as 12 stores in Canada and 25 stores in the Middle East. The company was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Washington. As of May 23, 2019, Papa Murphy's Holdings, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of MTY Franchising USA, Inc.
